The image shows a white sightseeing boat named "Windsor Sovereign" cruising along the River Thames in Windsor, England. The boat is positioned in the foreground, moving from left to right. It has a blue roof and several orange lifebuoys are visible along its sides. Passengers can be seen seated on the boat.

In the background, the historic Windsor Castle dominates the scene, perched on a hill. The castle's stone walls and towers are clearly visible, set against a clear blue sky. Lush green trees frame the castle on either side. 

